thread.title: Mukkie

author: Mukkie
title: Mukkie
text:
I loved it being a salesperson on my property and 2.5% commission.
First 3 months, I got 15 requests, during 2 months holiday I can manage this sell from overseas and luckily gone quite, that is good.
After holidays (Jan) I got 3 requests, one successful in Feb and 5% deposit. During under contract I got another 5 requests. We sold to the first deposit.
Good Fun each request gave us all different and interest questions. Next year selling house it will be different from sold this land. I am looking for joining Buymyplace again and good experience selling the house, more Fun.
It works and save 2.5% commission back in my pocket.
Mukkie
